    <li>Explore the repo: <a href="https://github.com/modelcontextprotocol/php-sdk" class="reference external" rel="external noopener noreferrer" target="_blank">github.com/modelcontextprotocol/php-sdk</a></li>
<li>Check open issues and examples</li>
<li>Try it out and share feedback</li>
<li>Join Symfony AI Hackathon for hands-on collaboration</li>
</ul>
</div>
</div>
<div class="section">
<h2 id="closing-notes"><a class="headerlink" href="#closing-notes" title="Permalink to this headline">Closing Notes</a></h2>
<p>We would like to thank <a href="https://experimentalworks.net/" class="reference external" rel="external noopener noreferrer" target="_blank">David Soria Parra</a> (Anthropic) and <a href="https://pronskiy.com/" class="reference external" rel="external noopener noreferrer" target="_blank">Roman Pronskiy</a> (PHP Foundation) for their initiative, and <a href="https://github.com/CodeWithKyrian" class="reference external" rel="external noopener noreferrer" target="_blank">Kyrian Obikwelu</a>, of PHP-MCP, for heading into this endeavor with us.</p>
<p>As part of this transition, the current symfony/ai MCP SDK package will be deprecated and removed.</p>
